name: LogarithmCalculator
0:
”Alexa, ask Logarithm Calculator what is the natural log of ten”
”Alexa, ask Logarithm Calculator what is the log base three of nine”
”Alexa, tell Logarithm Calculator to calculate the natural log of five hundred”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: logarithm calculator
des:
This skill allows Alexa to calculate logarithms for you. Do you ever wonder what the log base 7 of 55 is? Just use this skill. Logarithm Calculator supports positive whole numbers of reasonable size. 

Negative numbers, fractions, and decimals are not yet supported.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
